<h2>New Login Detected 🔐</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>
  We noticed a new login to your Novo Cars account.
</p>

<hr style="margin: 20px 0;" />

<p><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</p>

{{#if location}}
<p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
{{/if}}

{{#if device}}
<p><strong>Device:</strong> {{device}}</p>
{{/if}}

<hr style="margin: 20px 0;" />

<p>
  If this was you, no further action is needed.
</p>

<p>
  If you don’t recognize this activity, we recommend that you reset your password immediately.
</p>

<p style="margin: 20px 0;">
  <a 
    href="{{frontendUrl}}/auth/forgot-password"
    style="
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #000;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
    "
  >
    Secure Your Account
  </a>
</p>

<hr style="margin: 20px 0;" />

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777;">
  This notification helps keep your account secure.
</p>

<p>
  — Novo Cars Team
</p>